  "governance_notes": "All children preserve Stage1 and Stage2 fields. Global_vars and data_operations are synchronized from internal_leaf_accesses. ParseInput and RouteAction have no resource accesses, so their global_vars and data_operations are empty. TriggerBuild accesses both builds and artifacts; CheckStatus and ListBuilds only read builds; CancelBuild reads and writes builds. Constraints and acceptance criteria are derived from functional requirements and pre/postconditions. Traceability links each child to the relevant FRs.",
